---
// src/components/Features.astro
---

<!-- PLATFORM DIGITAL FEATURES SECTION -->
<section id="features" class="section reveal relative py-20">
	<!-- Section Header -->
	<div class="section-header flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-12">
		<div class="max-w-[700px]">
			<span class="text-xs font-extrabold text-[#C83E4D] tracking-[0.2em] block mb-2 uppercase">
				<span class="lang-id">SOLUSI DIGITAL PORTAL</span>
				<span class="lang-en">DIGITAL PORTAL SOLUTION</span>
			</span>
			<h2 class="section-title text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#0C3E3B] leading-tight">
				<span class="lang-id">Ekosistem Digital Pelestarian Tradisi</span>
				<span class="lang-en">Digital Ecosystem for Heritage Preservation</span>
			</h2>
		</div>
		<span class="text-sm font-bold text-[#5C6B69] tracking-wider uppercase mt-4 md:mt-0">
			PACU JALUR HUB
		</span>
	</div>

	<!-- 3 Columns Features Grid -->
	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
		
		<!-- Feature Card 1: Digital Archive -->
		<div class="feature-card glass-card rounded-[28px] flex flex-col justify-between border border-white/40 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[#E5A93B] hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden group" style="min-height: 400px; padding: 2rem;">
			<div class="absolute right-[-10px] bottom-[-20px] text-[10rem] font-heading font-black text-[#0C3E3B]/2 leading-none select-none pointer-events-none transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110">01</div>
			
			<div class="card-top relative z-10">
				<!-- Icon Wrapper -->
				<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#0C3E3B]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#0C3E3B] mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#0C3E3B] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-archive"><polyline points="21 8 21 21 3 21 3 8"></polyline><rect x="1" y="3" width="22" height="5"></rect><line x1="10" y1="12" x2="14" y2="12"></line></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-[#0C3E3B] mb-3">
					<span class="lang-id">Arsip & Pemetaan Digital</span>
					<span class="lang-en">Digital Archive & Mapping</span>
				</h3>
				<p class="text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-[#5C6B69] font-medium">
					<span class="lang-id">Digitalisasi komprehensif data spesifikasi perahu panjang, rekaman sejarah pacu legendaris, serta dokumentasi petuah lisan tetua adat Melayu Kuantan secara interaktif.</span>
					<span class="lang-en">Comprehensive digitalization of traditional longboat specs, historic race records, and interactive documentation of oral customs from Kuantan customary leaders.</span>
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="card-bottom mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#0C3E3B]/5 flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-extrabold relative z-10">
				<span class="uppercase" style="padding-left: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; font-weight: 800; color: #5C6B69;">CULTURAL ARCHIVE</span>
				<span class="text-[#E5A93B]">01</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Feature Card 2: Local Eco-Tourism -->
		<div class="feature-card glass-card rounded-[28px] flex flex-col justify-between border border-white/40 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[#E5A93B] hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden group" style="min-height: 400px; padding: 2rem;">
			<div class="absolute right-[-10px] bottom-[-20px] text-[10rem] font-heading font-black text-[#0C3E3B]/2 leading-none select-none pointer-events-none transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110">02</div>
			
			<div class="card-top relative z-10">
				<!-- Icon Wrapper -->
				<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#0C3E3B]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#0C3E3B] mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#0C3E3B] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-map-pin"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-[#0C3E3B] mb-3">
					<span class="lang-id">Koperasi Wisata Lokal</span>
					<span class="lang-en">Local Eco-Tourism Hub</span>
				</h3>
				<p class="text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-[#5C6B69] font-medium">
					<span class="lang-id">Menghubungkan langsung pelancong luar daerah dengan pemesanan homestay penduduk desa, pemandu lokal Tepian Narosa, dan industri kreatif miniatur perahu tanpa biaya komisi.</span>
					<span class="lang-en">Directly connecting travelers with local resident homestays, local guides around Tepian Narosa, and creative miniature boat craftsmen without platform service commissions.</span>
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="card-bottom mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#0C3E3B]/5 flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-extrabold relative z-10">
				<span class="uppercase" style="padding-left: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; font-weight: 800; color: #5C6B69;">COMMUNITY HUB</span>
				<span class="text-[#E5A93B]">02</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Feature Card 3: Reforestation Monitoring -->
		<div class="feature-card glass-card rounded-[28px] flex flex-col justify-between border border-white/40 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:border-[#E5A93B] hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden group" style="min-height: 400px; padding: 2rem;">
			<div class="absolute right-[-10px] bottom-[-20px] text-[10rem] font-heading font-black text-[#0C3E3B]/2 leading-none select-none pointer-events-none transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110">03</div>
			
			<div class="card-top relative z-10">
				<!-- Icon Wrapper -->
				<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#0C3E3B]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#0C3E3B] mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#0C3E3B] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-activity"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-[#0C3E3B] mb-3">
					<span class="lang-id">Sistem Reboisasi Digital</span>
					<span class="lang-en">Digital Reforestation Tracker</span>
				</h3>
				<p class="text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-[#5C6B69] font-medium">
					<span class="lang-id">Transparansi ekologi untuk mendata, memetakan, dan melacak pertumbuhan pohon pengganti (kayu Meranti) di hutan lindung demi menjamin kelestarian bahan baku kayu perahu utuh.</span>
					<span class="lang-en">Ecological transparency system to record, map, and track replacement hardwood tree growth (like Meranti) in conservation forests to sustain timber raw materials.</span>
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="card-bottom mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#0C3E3B]/5 flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-extrabold relative z-10">
				<span class="uppercase" style="padding-left: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; font-weight: 800; color: #5C6B69;">CONSERVATION TRUST</span>
				<span class="text-[#E5A93B]">03</span>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</section>
